I found that annoying as well, but have to agree with the melee-related comments. They have to kill big mobs to get the big weapons. Spells are our weapons. None of the spells in GoD are <span style="font-style: italic">required </span>to play the game (1).
<br />

<br />
The 50+ argument doesn't hold up for me either. You all should be farming the crap out of the XP named in Natimbi and doing the quests. The respawn is fast and gear is plentiful and of exceptionally high quality for players in their 50s.
<br />

<br />
Yes, the drop method and rate is inappropriate. It pains me to see something very valuable and rare rot because the proper class can't even be gotten to the drop, even if they are on.
