				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Sirulus Delon I like your post, well not all the profanity, but your points are well founed, and I argued them before. Spells should not be just for the ubers, and ancient spells I detest though I will get mine, just a matter of when as I am in a raiding guild that does nothing but raid 90% of the time. 
<br />

<br />
I have issues with some on this board that all their suggestions for class ballance reside in raiding fixes, and as some say, soloing get over it, it is a dead issue. Well with closed minds like that it sure is, because SoE is laughing at the class, hell we don't have to let them solo, let them fight internally. Than again you have the non raiders not in favor of raid improvements because they don't face those issues. Aggro, I don't get aggro so why worry? MS4 pet is a raid pet WTF we need a new pet for all mages NOT raid mages, and so the posts go. Than there is the groupng mage in many a zone are fine, till they hit LDoN hard and suddenly they see a lot of weakness that those in higher level guilds see daily.
<br />

<br />
So we fight amoung ourselves. It has to end. Mages swallow your pride and support changes that effct SOLOING GROUPING AND RAIDING. Yes ask for all damn 3 as so many classes ahve and got addressed.
<br />

<br />
Druids, got all 3 area's well covered. Wizards well we all know the top DPS on any raid, and can solo damn well. As for grouping, well 7000+ crit makes tham a very viable group member for me. Necro's say no more, soloing champs still. Raiding, well if the raid wipes a necro is usally able to res a cleric as thery FD'd and get the raid rolling again. as for grouping well if your in GoD, they are great. Emergency res'er, FD to drag bodies if need be, and with  neuro toxin and a pet, can do damn good FAST DD.
<br />

<br />
So as you see other classes had ALL 3 area's of the game well covered, we should ask for the same. Please don't anyone say we are asking to much. Just remember we are asking to improve the class FOR ALL magicians and there are exactly 3 play styles as I mentioned. Support them all in a uniform voice and stop giving SoE an excuse, that even mages don't support soloing, or raid improvements or grouping improvements, so damn since they can't agree on what to fix, we will fix nothing. Exactly what we have gotten for so damn long, and if there are coming fixes unless it addresses ALL mages concerns in all 3 area's it is not enough. Remember those mages are as important as you and your own play style are, even if you don't want to admit it. It is the facts. I can see raid mages bitching if it doesn't help them, and on the same not if it helps a raiding mage and not a soloing mage they will bitch, and the grouping mage gets a fix, it may piss off the raiding and soloing mages as it will not address their concerns. So cover all bases and support each other for a change.
